reactionGroups\": [\n        {\n          \"content\": \"EYES\",\n          \"users\": {\n            \"totalCount\": 1\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31863#issuecomment-4240276968\",\n      \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws78vYUl\",\n      \"author\": {\n        \"login\": \"dragon-ai-agent\"\n      },\n      \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n      \"body\": \"🤖 Working on it...\\n\\nFollow along: [View workflow run](https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/actions/runs/24372402903)\\n\\n*— @dragon-ai-agent*\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-13T23:34:34Z\",\n      \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n      \"isMinimized\": false,\n      \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n      \"reactionGroups\": [],\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31863#issuecomment-4240278821\",\n      \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws78vmB1\",\n      \"author\": {\n        \"login\": \"dragon-ai-agent\"\n      },\n      \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n      \"body\": \"Created new term **vesicle membrane tethering activity** (GO:7770062) as a child of [GO:0140177 membrane-membrane adaptor activity](https://www.ebi.ac.uk/QuickGO/term/GO:0140177).\\n\\n**Definition:** A membrane-membrane adaptor activity that provides the first point of contact and physically bridges the vesicle membrane and its target membrane prior to vesicle docking and fusion.\\n\\n**References:**\\n- `PMID:19887069` — Sztul & Lupashin 2009, *FEBS Lett*, \\\"Role of vesicle tethering factors in the ER-Golgi membrane traffic\\\" (as requested)\\n- `PMID:19575650` — Yu & Hughson 2010, *Annu Rev Cell Dev Biol*, \\\"Tethering factors as organizers of intracellular vesicular traffic\\\" — a broad review covering tethering factors across intracellular trafficking pathways, including the plasma-membrane exocyst and CATCHR-family complexes (Munc13 has a CATCHR/MUN-domain fold and is a key synaptic vesicle tethering factor)\\n\\nA note on the second reference: you asked for an article that \\\"also covers synaptic vesicle transport and targeting.\\\" Yu & Hughson 2010 is a general review that includes synaptic-relevant tethers (exocyst, CATCHR/Munc13) within its broader scope. If you'd prefer a more synapse-focused companion reference, I'd suggest `PMID:23164531` (Hallermann & Silver 2013, *Trends Neurosci*, \\\"Sustaining rapid vesicular release at active zones: potential roles for vesicle tethering\\\") or `PMID:22794257` (Südhof 2012, *Neuron*, \\\"The presynaptic active zone\\\"). Happy to swap or add — just let me know.\\n\\nSynonyms added:\\n- `vesicle membrane tether activity` (EXACT)\\n- `vesicle tethering activity` (EXACT)\\n\\nPR: geneontology/go-ontology#31895\\n\\n---\\n🤖 **Generated by @dragon-ai-agent**\\n- Model: `claude-opus-4-6`\\n- Agent harness: claude-code\\n- Triggered by: @raymond91125\\n- Run: [View workflow run](https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/actions/runs/24372402903)\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-13T23:49:27Z\",\n      \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n      \"isMinimized\": false,\n      \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n      \"reactionGroups\": [],\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31863#issuecomment-4240334965\",\n      \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws78vuWI\",\n      \"author\": {\n        \"login\": \"raymond91125\"\n      },\n      \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n      \"body\": \"@dragon-ai-agent please extend the definition of GO:0140177 membrane-membrane adaptor activity to include vesicle. \\\"The binding activity of a molecule that brings together two membranes, either via membrane lipid binding or by interacting with a membrane protein, to establish or maintain the localization of the protein, protein complex, vesicle or organelle.\\\"\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-13T23:58:45Z\",\n 